					<li>Exclusive levels and HD resolution for the Steam version</li>                        
					<li>Exclusive BETA level editor for the Steam version</li>                        
					<li>Exclusive Steam Achievements</li>                         </ul>','<p>                        Eternity''s Child, a quirky, hand drawn next generation 2D platformer is based on a fairy tale by Luc Bernard. It arrives on Steam with exclusive Steam Only levels and HD Resolution.                        </p>                        
