                    <p>&nbsp;</p>
                    <img src="http://storefront.steampowered.com/v/gfx/apps/36180/extras/cm_logo.jpg" align="left">
                    <p>Welcome to Cake Mania®! Jill, our hero, has returned from culinary school, only to find her beloved grandparents'' bakery closed down. Business has taken a drastic downturn because a new Mega-Mart store opened in the neighborhood.</p>
